{"id":2409,"date":"2019-09-06T17:29:08","date_gmt":"2019-09-06T17:29:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/?p=2409"},"modified":"2019-12-09T08:55:59","modified_gmt":"2019-12-09T01:55:59","slug":"pr-co-ban","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/pr-co-ban.html\/","title":{"rendered":"Nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 PR c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft trong n\u0103m 2020"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_36 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">N\u1ed9i Dung<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><label for=\"item\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"item\"><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/pr-co-ban.html\/#Vay_PR_co_nghia_la_gi\" title=\"V\u1eady PR c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\">V\u1eady PR c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/pr-co-ban.html\/#Nguoi_lam_PR_la_nhung_chuyen_gia_ke_chuyen\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m PR l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chuy\u00ean gia k\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec7n.\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m PR l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chuy\u00ean gia k\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec7n.<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/pr-co-ban.html\/#Cong_cu_cua_chung_toi\" title=\"C\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u00a0\">C\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u00a0<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/pr-co-ban.html\/#Su_khac_biet_giua_PR_va_quang_cao\" title=\"S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa PR v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\">S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa PR v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/pr-co-ban.html\/#Cau_chuyen_thuc_te\" title=\"C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/pr-co-ban.html\/#Lieu_co_thuoc_do_nao_cho_PR\" title=\"Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o n\u00e0o cho PR?\">Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o n\u00e0o cho PR?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>Ng\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p PR qu\u00e1 b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ai th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e2ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p><i><\/i>R\u1ea5t \u00edt ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n t\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m PR. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t, c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng hay m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t hay m\u1ed9t c\u00f4 gi\u00e1o, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p>B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n<strong> nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 PR c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft trong n\u0103m 2020<\/strong> nh\u00e9<strong>.\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><em>H\u00e3y theo ch\u00e2n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00e0o!<\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Vay_PR_co_nghia_la_gi\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 110%;\"><strong>V\u1eady PR c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b><\/b><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-7545 aligncenter\" src=\"http:\/\/prchuyennghiep.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/bigstock-162396293-1024x565-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/prchuyennghiep.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/bigstock-162396293-1024x565-1.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/prchuyennghiep.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/bigstock-162396293-1024x565-1-300x166.jpg 300w, http:\/\/prchuyennghiep.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/bigstock-162396293-1024x565-1-768x424.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"565\" \/>PR c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. B\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf ngay trong to\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i ph\u1ea1m vi m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng, mua s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 ghi nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p><i>\u201cPR l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eb1m x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.\u201d<\/i>\u00a0\u2013 C\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng quan h\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9 PRSA \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd sau v\u00e0i ngh\u00ecn l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec7 tr\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nguoi_lam_PR_la_nhung_chuyen_gia_ke_chuyen\"><\/span><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m PR l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chuy\u00ean gia k\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec7n.<\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>H\u1ecd thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt r\u1ed3i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c.<\/p>\n<p>PR c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, n\u00e2ng cao hay x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng danh ti\u1ebfng th\u00f4ng qua ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1i ch\u00fang, m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u01a1 quan truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed9t h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean PR gi\u1ecfi s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n t\u00edch c\u01a1 quan t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0o trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. Khi c\u00f3 tin t\u1ee9c x\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u thi\u1ec7t h\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2410\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2410\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2410\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eefng-hi\u1ec3u-bi\u1ebft-c\u01a1-b\u1ea3n-v\u1ec1-pr.png\" alt=\"nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 pr\" width=\"825\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eefng-hi\u1ec3u-bi\u1ebft-c\u01a1-b\u1ea3n-v\u1ec1-pr.png 870w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eefng-hi\u1ec3u-bi\u1ebft-c\u01a1-b\u1ea3n-v\u1ec1-pr-300x121.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eefng-hi\u1ec3u-bi\u1ebft-c\u01a1-b\u1ea3n-v\u1ec1-pr-768x309.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2410\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">PR n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cong_cu_cua_chung_toi\"><\/span><em>C\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u00a0<\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Vi\u1ebft v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t h\u00e0nh th\u00f4ng c\u00e1o b\u00e1o ch\u00ed<\/li>\n<li>B\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u<\/li>\n<li>Vi\u1ebft th\u01b0 m\u1eddi th\u1ea7u (\u00edt trang tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng c\u00e1o b\u00e1o ch\u00ed) v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c v\u00e0 g\u1eedi tr\u1ef1c \u00a0ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o<\/li>\n<li>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 quan h\u1ec7 truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng<\/li>\n<li>Ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec1 l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c ho\u1eb7c th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Su_khac_biet_giua_PR_va_quang_cao\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 110%;\"><b>S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa PR v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/b><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b><\/b><b><\/b><b><\/b><b><\/b><b><\/b><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7548\" src=\"http:\/\/prchuyennghiep.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/webico.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1021px) 100vw, 1021px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/prchuyennghiep.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/webico.png 1021w, http:\/\/prchuyennghiep.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/webico-300x132.png 300w, http:\/\/prchuyennghiep.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/webico-768x338.png 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1021\" height=\"450\" \/>\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t ph\u00ed v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t ph\u00ed, gi\u1eefa s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i, gi\u1eefa tin c\u1eady v\u00e0 nghi ng\u1edd, PR tr\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb tuy\u1ec7t trong khi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ch\u01b0a to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n b\u1eb1ng.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng n\u00f3i:\u00a0<i>\u201cQu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i chi tr\u1ea3 c\u00f2n s\u1ef1 lan truy\u1ec1n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n\u201d<\/i><\/p>\n<p>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng so s\u00e1nh b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o:<\/p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 180px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 20px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\"><b>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/b><\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\"><b>PR<\/b><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 20px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">Tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">Lan truy\u1ec1n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 20px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ee7 s\u00f3ng<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u00f2ng tin<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 20px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">C\u00f4ng ch\u00fang ho\u00e0i nghi<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">B\u00ean th\u1ee9 ba<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 20px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">S\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp s\u1eb5n<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m, c\u1ea7n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 20px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">Ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 20px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u00a0h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c thu h\u00fat<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">PR s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 20px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">\u0110\u1eaft h\u01a1n<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">\u00cdt \u0111\u1eaft h\u01a1n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 20px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">\u201cMua s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y\u201d<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 20px;\">\u201cC\u00e1i n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3. C\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty PR t\u00ednh ph\u00ed h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thu\u00ea \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, trong khi, qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o th\u00ec r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cau_chuyen_thuc_te\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><em>C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf<\/em><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>M\u1ed9t kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng mua m\u1ed9t trang qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean cu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1p ch\u00ed h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 125 ngh\u00ecn \u0111\u00f4.<\/p>\n<p>\u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t tr\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o c\u01a1n b\u00e3o cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi, \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ee7 s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn \u0111a chi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra.<\/p>\n<p>Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean c\u00e1c trang b\u00e1o <em>New York Times, Forbes<\/em> v\u00e0 <em>Reuters<\/em> \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi ng\u00f4n lu\u1eadn trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi t\u1eeb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u1edbi ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 uy t\u00edn v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc.<\/p>\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf ra 125 ngh\u00ecn \u0111\u00f4 nh\u01b0ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf khi b\u1ea1n \u0111o \u0111\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng hay th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0nh th\u00eam cho nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft th\u1ebf s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m.<\/p>\n<p>V\u00e0 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft m\u1ecdi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ea7n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n th\u00ec m\u1edbi thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1edfi v\u00ec l\u1ee3i \u00edch l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n nghe nh\u01b0 \u201cB\u1ea1n l\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2411\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2411\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2411\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eefng-l\u1ee3i-\u00edch-pr-mang-l\u1ea1i-kh\u00f4ng-k\u00e9m-ph\u1ea7n-c\u00e1c-chi\u1ebfn-d\u1ecbch-kh\u00e1c-\u0111em-\u0111\u1ebfn.jpg\" alt=\"nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 pr\" width=\"825\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eefng-l\u1ee3i-\u00edch-pr-mang-l\u1ea1i-kh\u00f4ng-k\u00e9m-ph\u1ea7n-c\u00e1c-chi\u1ebfn-d\u1ecbch-kh\u00e1c-\u0111em-\u0111\u1ebfn.jpg 345w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eefng-l\u1ee3i-\u00edch-pr-mang-l\u1ea1i-kh\u00f4ng-k\u00e9m-ph\u1ea7n-c\u00e1c-chi\u1ebfn-d\u1ecbch-kh\u00e1c-\u0111em-\u0111\u1ebfn-300x127.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2411\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch pr mang l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch kh\u00e1c \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n b\u1ecf ra v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0 c\u00e1c k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p>V\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m PR th\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng, g\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o m\u1ed1i li\u00ean k\u1ebft b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng khi c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn b\u1edfi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m PR cho b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i nghe.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Lieu_co_thuoc_do_nao_cho_PR\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><em>Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o n\u00e0o cho PR?<\/em><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7553\" src=\"http:\/\/prchuyennghiep.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/A_ECCM-1118_prbrief_Data-you-can-measure.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 963px) 100vw, 963px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/prchuyennghiep.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/A_ECCM-1118_prbrief_Data-you-can-measure.png 963w, http:\/\/prchuyennghiep.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/A_ECCM-1118_prbrief_Data-you-can-measure-300x129.png 300w, http:\/\/prchuyennghiep.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/A_ECCM-1118_prbrief_Data-you-can-measure-768x331.png 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"963\" height=\"415\" \/><span style=\"font-size: inherit;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t khoa h\u1ecdc ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh, b\u1ea3ng t\u00ednh v\u00e0 \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra. Ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00e2y \u201cch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd\u201d nh\u1ea5t trong ng\u00e0nh PR.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2412\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2412\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2412\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/\u0110\u1ecbnh-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-PR-v\u1eabn-c\u00f2n-\u0111ang-g\u00e2y-ra-tranh-c\u00e3i.jpg\" alt=\"nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 PR\" width=\"825\" height=\"431\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/\u0110\u1ecbnh-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-PR-v\u1eabn-c\u00f2n-\u0111ang-g\u00e2y-ra-tranh-c\u00e3i.jpg 1201w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/\u0110\u1ecbnh-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-PR-v\u1eabn-c\u00f2n-\u0111ang-g\u00e2y-ra-tranh-c\u00e3i-300x157.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/\u0110\u1ecbnh-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-PR-v\u1eabn-c\u00f2n-\u0111ang-g\u00e2y-ra-tranh-c\u00e3i-768x402.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/\u0110\u1ecbnh-l\u01b0\u1ee3ng-PR-v\u1eabn-c\u00f2n-\u0111ang-g\u00e2y-ra-tranh-c\u00e3i-1024x535.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2412\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1ecbnh l\u01b0\u1ee3ng PR v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang g\u00e2y ra tranh c\u00e3i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdn ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc Barcelona \u2013 b\u1ea3y h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u1ef1 nguy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp b\u1edfi c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia trong ng\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111o l\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch PR. Nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2010 khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean t\u1eeb 33 qu\u1ed1c gia g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ea1i Barcelona.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110o l\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3y nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p, t\u1ed1n th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c thu\u00ea m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng ty b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c cao c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7n c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng. C\u00e1c nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ng\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p PR qu\u00e1 b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ai th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e2ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. R\u1ea5t \u00edt ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n t\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m PR. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t, c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2413,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[51],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>\u0110\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 PR cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u | \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media xin gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u b\u1ea1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a, \u00fd ngh\u0129a m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 PR m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft trong n\u0103m 2020. V\u00e0 h\u00e3y theo ch\u00e2n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3...\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/pr-co-ban.html\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"vi_VN\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 PR c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft trong n\u0103m 2020\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media xin gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u b\u1ea1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a, \u00fd ngh\u0129a m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 PR m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\